      </div>

      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-num">✗</div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Skip Koala AI if</h3>
        <h4 class="bento-sub">You're a <span class="accent">local business or need hands-off publishing</span> without manual triggers.</h4>
        <p class="bento-desc">No GBP, no Maps ranking, no scheduled publishing. Every article needs a manual submit. theStacc automates the full stack from writing to going live.</p>
        <div class="bento-cta">See why theStacc fits better <span class="arrow">↓</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS KOALA AI -->
  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">What is Koala AI</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">A two-product AI writing platform built for <span class="accent">affiliate and niche content.</span></h2>
      <p>Koala AI launched in 2022 as a two-product platform. KoalaWriter generates SEO-optimized long-form articles using real-time SERP analysis and live internet data. KoalaChat is a web-enabled conversational research assistant. The platform particularly serves affiliate marketers and niche site operators who need high-volume content with low hallucination risk.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 16px;">What sets Koala apart from generic AI writers is the data layer. Before generating a single word, KoalaWriter pulls live internet data, checks current SERP results, and incorporates fresh information into the output. That reduces the hallucinated statistics and outdated pricing that plague pure-training-data tools.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 16px;">The Amazon affiliate mode is genuinely differentiated — no other tool we tested handles ASIN-based product review content this cleanly. Drop in an ASIN, and Koala pulls specs, features, and comparison angles directly from Amazon without any manual data entry. For affiliate marketers building review sites, that alone justifies the subscription.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROS / CONS -->
  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">The honest pros & cons</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">What Koala AI gets right — <span class="accent">and where it lets you down.</span></h2>
      <p>Tested across affiliate reviews, niche site articles, and YouTube-to-blog conversions to find the real edges.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">Pros</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Where Koala AI shines</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Five genuine strengths worth paying for.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Best Amazon affiliate review generation</h4>
              <p>No competitor handles ASIN-based content as cleanly. Drop in a product ASIN and Koala pulls specs, features, and comparison angles automatically — no manual research needed.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Real-time data integration</h4>
              <p>Pulls live internet data before generating, reducing hallucination and keeping statistics and product information current. A meaningful edge over pure training-data tools.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>WordPress auto-publishing</h4>
              <p>Direct upload to WordPress across multiple sites eliminates copy-paste workflows. Users consistently call this a workflow game-changer in reviews.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>API access on all plans</h4>
              <p>Even the $9 Essentials tier includes API access, enabling custom content workflow automation. Most competitors gate API behind much higher plan tiers.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>YouTube-to-blog conversion</h4>
              <p>Transforms video transcripts into structured blog posts in about two minutes. Solid option for creators who want to extend their video content reach without doubling production effort.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-col before">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">Cons</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Where Koala AI falls short</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Five honest weaknesses we ran into.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Confusing word credit model</h4>
              <p>Premium AI models consume 2x word credits, depleting budgets twice as fast as users expect. The $49 Professional plan runs out at half the volume most people assume.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Real cost is higher than listed</h4>
              <p>Quality output at 30 articles per month effectively requires the $99 Boost plan, not the $49 Professional plan — because premium model usage burns credits at 2x the rate.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>No built-in keyword research</h4>
              <p>You need a separate tool — Ahrefs, Semrush, or equivalent at $99–$119/month — for keyword identification and content planning. Koala generates; it doesn't strategize.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Manual triggering required for every article</h4>
              <p>No calendar-based automation. Every article needs a manual submit. You can't set a publishing schedule and walk away.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>No local SEO capability</h4>
              <p>Google Business Profile, citation tools, and Maps ranking features are entirely absent. Local service businesses get nothing relevant here.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS ROW -->
  <section>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">$9<span class="accent">+</span></div><div class="stat-label">Starting monthly price</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">4.1<span class="accent">/5</span></div><div class="stat-label">Average user rating · 428 reviews</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">2×<span class="accent"></span></div><div class="stat-label">Credit cost for premium AI models</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">9<span class="accent">+</span></div><div class="stat-label">Pricing tiers available</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES IN DEPTH -->
  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">Features in depth</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">Every major <span class="accent">Koala AI feature</span>, tested.</h2>
      <p>What's actually in the box — and how each piece performed in real testing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>KoalaWriter</h4>
              <p>Generates 1,500–5,000 word articles from a keyword using competitive SERP analysis before production. It incorporates structure patterns and terminology from top-ranking pages, which produces more search-relevant output than keyword-only tools.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Amazon product review mode</h4>
              <p>Accepts ASINs or product URLs, automatically extracts specs, features, and comparison angles, and builds full affiliate review articles without any manual data entry. In our tests, this produced the most useful affiliate content of any tool at this price point.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>KoalaChat</h4>
              <p>A separate conversational AI interface with real-time web search and file analysis. Runs on message quotas independent from your word credit pool, so heavy chat usage doesn't eat into writing capacity.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Deep research mode</h4>
              <p>Available on Professional and above — takes 2–4 minutes instead of under 60 seconds and produces more comprehensive competitive analysis before generating. The quality difference is noticeable on high-stakes content.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>YouTube transcript conversion</h4>
              <p>Transforms a video URL into a formatted blog post with headers and transitions. Takes about two minutes. Light editorial polish is needed, but it's a solid workflow for video-first creators.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">06</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Multi-AI model selection</h4>
              <p>Choose GPT-5 Mini (efficient, 1x credits), GPT-5.2 (premium, 2x credits), or Claude 4.5 Sonnet (premium, 2x credits) per article. Important to understand the credit implications before defaulting to premium models on every piece.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">07</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Automatic internal linking</h4>
              <p>Professional and above scans your existing content and inserts relevant internal links during generation. Saves meaningful time on sites with 50+ articles where manual internal linking becomes impractical.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="cost-section">
    <div class="cost-header">
      <span class="label-pill">Pricing</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">What Koala AI <span class="accent">actually costs.</span></h2>
      <p>Nine pricing tiers from $9 to $2,000/month. The key detail: premium AI model usage burns 2x credits. Factor that in before choosing a plan.</p>
