    <div class="cost-table">
      <div class="cost-row head">
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell">Tier</div>
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell">Koala AI</div>
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell">Word credits</div>
        <div class="cost-cell head-cell brand">theStacc equivalent</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="cost-cell label"><div class="vert">Essentials</div><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Solo bloggers</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price">$9</div><div class="per">per month</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">15,000 words · 250 chat msgs</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell brand"><div class="price brand">$49</div><div class="per">starter · all-in</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="cost-cell label"><div class="vert">Professional</div><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Active publishers</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price">$49</div><div class="per">per month</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">100,000 words · 1,000 chat msgs</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell brand"><div class="price brand">$99</div><div class="per">pro · all-in</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="cost-cell label"><div class="vert">Boost</div><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Agencies · teams</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price">$99</div><div class="per">per month</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell"><div class="price" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">250,000 words · 2,500 chat msgs</div></div>
        <div class="cost-cell brand"><div class="price brand">$199</div><div class="per">scale · all-in</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-savings">
        <div class="big">The $49 plan looks like enough — until premium models halve your word budget.</div>
        <div class="lbl">Most serious users end up at $99 once they account for 2x credit costs on quality models.</div>
      </div>
