      <h2 class="h-lg">Koala AI generates. <span class="accent">theStacc publishes.</span></h2>
      <p>Two different promises for two different buyers. Here's the side-by-side.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cost-table" style="overflow-x: auto;">
      <table style="width: 100%; min-width: 700px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px;">
        <thead>
